www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/sk/tc_chi/meetings/dcmeetings/dc_meetings_audio.php?meeting_id=16362\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fsk%2Ftc_chi%2Fmeetings%2Fdcmeetings%2Fdc_meetings_audio.php%3Fmeeting_id%3D16362&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2Fhgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=555ad17e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/sk/tc_chi/meetings/dcmeetings/dc_meetings_audio.php?meeting_id=16362</a><br />\n<br />\n(16) 反對《2019 年逃犯及刑事事宜相互法律協助法例(修訂)條例草案》，要求使用一次性移交疑犯，處理台灣殺人案 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/sk/doc/2016_2019/common/dc_meetings_audio/16362/DC_19_3_v26.mp3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.districtcouncils.gov.hk%2Fsk%2Fdoc%2F2016_2019%2Fcommon%2Fdc_meetings_audio%2F16362%2FDC_19_3_v26.mp3&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2Fhgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=0588b878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.districtcouncils.gov.hk/sk/doc/2016_2019/common/dc_meetings_audio/16362/DC_19_3_v26.mp3</a><br />\n22:00開始<br />\n:「表決結果，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">贊成6票</span></span>，反對12票，棄權1票，原動議不獲通過。」"},{"pid":"1b0ad54f17f0e5b7733c57ddefdf6e13ffefc11d","tid":1229912,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:42:40.000Z","msg":"咖哩飯呢條垃圾永遠唔會再係我全家屋企人拎到一票"},{"pid":"8b9dd353d6fa414f65e36c6afd34c9992eca30d9","tid":1229912,"uid":60615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:49:23.000Z","msg":"范國西狗改不了吃屎"},{"pid":"2022bbf535f5eedd7b61fc8352a4ff3865624876","tid":1229912,"uid":171192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1b0ad54f17f0e5b7733c57ddefdf6e13ffefc11d","tid":1229912,"uid":25900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:42:40.000Z","msg":"咖哩飯呢條垃圾永遠唔會再係我全家屋企人拎到一票"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:49:51.000Z","msg":"都話泛民有班仆街信唔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隔離post炒哂車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a635ff687315571b3355054fc8511bb5f641517f","tid":1229912,"uid":36911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T05:50:25.000Z","msg":"左邊張圖唔代表係真喎<br />\n有冇會議記錄先"},{"pid":"fd5107307f893ba2411282d4c72cec3317f91a87","tid":1229912,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:02:02.000Z","msg":"方國珊不支持范國威議案(棄權), 支持張展鵬修正案<br />\n<br />\n方國珊都認左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/124853124283126/photos/a.1836295296472225/1836555786446176/?type=3&amp;comment_id=1836903356411419&amp;comment_tracking=%7B%22tn%22%3A%22R%22%7D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F124853124283126%2Fphotos%2Fa.1836295296472225%2F1836555786446176%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26comment_id%3D1836903356411419%26comment_tracking%3D%257B%2522tn%2522%253A%2522R%2522%257D&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2Fhgx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=e6787144\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/124853124283126/photos/a.1836295296472225/1836555786446176/?type=3&amp;comment_id=1836903356411419&amp;comment_tracking=%7B%22tn%22%3A%22R%22%7D</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n方國珊 <br />\n「唔同意措辭字眼意思先會有修訂嘅理由，假如對原動議投下贊成，那為何作出修訂？<br />\n<br />\n本人在修訂動議明確表明立場，反對現行的逃犯條例，<strong>但范國威就指本人沒有就他那措辭有問題的原動議投票=唔理港人利益=出賣港人？</strong><br />\n是其是，非其非係指岩嘅就要認同，唔岩嘅就時要反對，我對范國威的措辭有保留，但無可能就議題本質投反對，就唯有離席，修訂動議內容已足見我的立場。<br />\n反而我好疑惑，無論係修定動議定原動議都被否決，范議員點解唔貼曬兩個出嚟話畀大家知投反對票的人有幾可惡？<br />\n我幫佢答：1. 佢認為修定動議唔係反對緊逃犯條件<br />\n2. 佢想形造本人或其他議員出賣港人的效果"},{"pid":"6d1d86b98981471fb06f97d0cd09510d74c49cf0","tid":1229912,"uid":60023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:06:14.000Z","msg":"方國珊真係冇投"},{"pid":"dee3c744c547328a39b21b7c4ac58b3161a6d5ed","tid":1229912,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6d1d86b98981471fb06f97d0cd09510d74c49cf0","tid":1229912,"uid":60023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:06:14.000Z","msg":"方國珊真係冇投"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:07:54.000Z","msg":"方國珊無投范國威議案(棄權), 但投票支持張展鵬修正案"}]}